Common viva questions
1. What is HTML?
HTML stands for HyperText Markup Language.
2. Which tag is used to create a form?
<form>
3. Which input type is used for name?
type="text"
4. Which input type is used for email?
type="email"
5. Why is type="email" used?
It accepts email format input.
6. Which input type is used for gender?
type="radio"
7. Why do both radio buttons have the same name?
So only one option can be selected.
8. Which input type is used for date of birth?
type="date"
9. Which input type creates the submit button?
type="submit"
